| # | Назва | Scope | Залежить від |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | [Foundation](./phase-1-foundation.md) | packages/types, User Schema, ENV, bcrypt | — |
| 2 | [Password Auth](./phase-2-password-auth.md) | check-email, login/password, brute force | 1 |
